{"id": 3110, "genre": 1000, "title": "都 2020 年了，哪些事让你意识到科技似乎并没有想象中发展得那么好？", "description": "对比曾经那些对 2020 年的畅想，未免有点失落。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images ）", "record_count": 12182, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20200101215314dfoubgQViWI3CcxS.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-01T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6157, "title": "都 2020 年了，哪些事让你意识到科技似乎并没有想象中发展得那么好？", "content": "都2020年了，生活中哪些方面让你意识到科技并没有想象中发展的那么好？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 351343, "content": "新型家电的卖点，无外乎就是“纳米”和“负离子”", "image": "img/option/option/20200101215712T2rlt5vxaJOeUqKo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351344, "content": "科幻作品好像也陷入了虫洞/量子/机器人/复制人的老套路", "image": "img/option/option/20200101215904zMvEbQn9fC0m3tjy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351346, "content": "新出的手机机型，反反复复只能在摄像头上做文章", "image": "img/option/option/20200101221103x1v7iVXHYtGy5d6n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351347, "content": "提到汽车就是新能源/自动驾驶，没有什么靠谱的新理念出现", "image": "img/option/option/20200101221315wQZdqexcjWItM1X6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351348, "content": "环保/新药/基因天天说，但人类好像并没有因此活得更快乐", "image": "img/option/option/20200101221630bCSA1YV5GDFgjRom.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351349, "content": "护肤黑科技，无非就是焕发啊新生啊各种大词堆砌", "image": "img/option/option/20200101222120QyUdWVo9OeHT64sl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351350, "content": "电子产品除了变薄了点儿之外，bug 什么的还是一点没少", "image": "img/option/option/20200101221856iSpdRzC9wkDhl2xs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 351351, "content": "智能产品还是不够智能，比如永远听不懂我在说啥的语音助手", "image": "img/option/option/20200101222311pcxBukg5avmtJ0S8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}